  VALUES ('eafac516-1689-4ad2-8423-ba28594b0f94', 'chainsaw-man-meme-templates-2945', 'Chainsaw Man Meme Templates', 'Chainsawmanmeme is an online tool designed specifically for generating meme images based onChainsaw Man. In essence, it is an “IP-themed meme generator.” Users can quickly add text using pre-made character templates and generate images for sharing on social platforms to express emotions or create lightweight entertainment content. Unlike general-purpose AI image generators, it focuses on a single anime IP and uses a template-based output approach. This makes it more of a plug-and-play meme tool rather than a creative design platform. Compared to complex design software, it significantly reduces the creation steps, but also limits creative freedom, making it better suited for fast generation and sharing.', '', 'https://chainsawmanmeme.com/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://chainsawmanmeme.com/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.freeai.run/og.png', 'freemium', '[]'::jsonb, cat_id, false, 'published', 'freeai.run', 0)
