  VALUES ('b42c9afe-98b3-4570-98c2-7296946976b3', 'perplexity', 'Perplexity', 'Perplexity.ai is an AI-powered "generative search and answer platform" that searches the web in real time and provides concise answers to user queries. Unlike simple keyword searches, it understands natural language questions and extracts and organizes relevant information. Answers may include source links, allowing users to trace the origins of the information. Compared to traditional search engines and AI chatbots, Perplexity emphasizes the experience of "information discovery and instant answers," making it particularly suitable for research and fact-checking purposes. Perplexity offers both free and paid plans, with options to use more advanced models, search internal documents, and analyze files.', '', 'https://www.perplexity.ai/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.perplexity.ai/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.freeai.run/og.png', 'freemium', '[]'::jsonb, cat_id, false, 'published', 'freeai.run', 0)
