  VALUES ('2960ffb6-53bd-41c3-9cbd-a6d0809599ea', 'china-ai', 'China AI', 'ChinaAI.app is a directory and information aggregation website focused on the “China AI ecosystem.” It collects, categorizes, and showcases domestic AI products and related resources. Its core purpose is to let users browse different types of AI tools (such as image generation, writing, and video) on a single page and quickly navigate to each product’s official website. Compared with general AI directories, it is more focused on the Chinese market and Chinese-language tools, making it suitable for discovering domestic AI products or understanding local AI developments. Overall, it is positioned as an “entry-point directory” rather than a platform for in-depth reviews or a single-tool service.', '', 'https://www.chinaai.app/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.chinaai.app/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.freeai.run/og.png', 'freemium', '[]'::jsonb, cat_id, false, 'published', 'freeai.run', 0)
