  VALUES ('95c99a1e-f508-433f-9693-d52e4530f665', 'vo4-video-ai', 'vo4 video ai', 'VO4 AI is a web-based AI video generation tool primarily used toconvert text descriptions or a single image into short video content. It does not offer traditional timeline editing or complex post-production features. Instead, it relies on predefined video generation models to automatically handle motion, camera transitions, and visual style consistency.In terms of product positioning, VO4 AI is closer to an “automated video generator” than a professional video editing application. Its core value lies in lowering the barrier to video creation, enabling users to quickly produce usable video results without dealing with clip editing, keyframes, or effect settings.Tools like this are typically suited for scenarios where production efficiency is important, but fine-grained control is not a priority—such as concept demonstrations, content drafts, or short video asset generation.', '', 'https://www.vo4ai.art/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.vo4ai.art/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.freeai.run/og.png', 'freemium', '[]'::jsonb, cat_id, false, 'published', 'freeai.run', 0)
