  VALUES ('2b28c05f-950c-493c-9912-3fac9afb5a44', 'seedream-6', 'seedream 6', 'Seedream6.app is an AI-poweredimage generation and editing platformthat allows users to quickly create high-resolution visual content using text prompts or uploaded reference images. It primarily addresses the challenge for non-professional designers to produce creative images or product visuals in a short time. Unlike traditional text-to-image tools, Seedream6 supports multi-image blending, style replication, and high-resolution output, enabling users to create directly in the browser without installing a client or mastering complex design software. This tool is especially suitable for scenarios like quickly producing social media graphics, marketing materials, illustrations, or product showcase images, but it is not ideal for professional projects that require detailed hand-drawn work or long-term iterative design.', '', 'https://www.seedream6.app/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.seedream6.app/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.freeai.run/og.png', 'freemium', '[]'::jsonb, cat_id, false, 'published', 'freeai.run', 0)
