  VALUES ('c88606ac-b24a-4141-92a5-20c049b4bca1', 'hailuo-30', 'hailuo 3.0', 'Hailuo‑3.com is an online AI video generation platform, designed to quickly convert text descriptions or static images into short video content. It primarily addresses the complexity and time-consuming nature of traditional video production, allowing users to create visual works without installing software or mastering editing skills. Compared to other video generation tools, Hailuo‑3.com emphasizesfast, one-click generationandimage-driven video creation, making it ideal for social media content, educational presentations, or product showcases where efficiency is key. Its usage scope is clear—it is not suitable for complex editing or feature-length production, but rather for rapid generation of short videos and dynamic clips.', '', 'https://www.hailuo-3.com/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.hailuo-3.com/?utm_source=freeai.run', 'https://www.freeai.run/og.png', 'freemium', '[]'::jsonb, cat_id, false, 'published', 'freeai.run', 0)
